@startuml xray_request_state
!theme plain
title X-ray Request State Chart Diagram

[*] --> Created

Created --> Pending : submit()\n[Specialist Doctor submits request]

Pending --> InProgress : startProcessing()\n[Technician begins processing]

InProgress --> ImageUploaded : uploadImage()\n[Technician uploads X-ray image]

ImageUploaded --> ProcessingAnalysis : analyze()\n[AI model processes image]

ProcessingAnalysis --> AnalysisComplete : analysisComplete()\n[AI returns prediction]

AnalysisComplete --> Completed : storeResults()\n[Results saved to database]

' Error transitions
ImageUploaded --> InProgress : invalidImage()\n[Image rejected - not X-ray]
ProcessingAnalysis --> InProgress : processingError()\n[AI processing failed]

' Self-transitions
Pending --> Pending : updatePriority()\n[Request priority changed]
InProgress --> InProgress : retakeImage()\n[Image quality issues]

' Notes
note right of Created
  Request initialized
  with patient and doctor info
end note

note right of Pending
  Waiting for technician
  to process request
end note

note right of InProgress
  Technician actively
  working on request
end note

note right of ImageUploaded
  Valid X-ray image
  uploaded to system
end note

note right of ProcessingAnalysis
  AI model analyzing
  for cardiomegaly
end note

note right of AnalysisComplete
  Prediction and confidence
  score generated
end note

note right of Completed
  Results available
  for doctor review
end note

@enduml